query:
UPDATE room_types 
SET images = CASE 
  WHEN id = 360001 THEN 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dqhct1qfx/image/upload/w_500,h_400,c_fill,q_auto,f_auto/v1706000000/hotels/luxury-double-room.jpg'
  WHEN id = 360002 THEN 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dqhct1qfx/image/upload/w_500,h_400,c_fill,q_auto,f_auto/v1706000000/hotels/standard-double-room.jpg'
  WHEN id = 360003 THEN 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dqhct1qfx/image/upload/w_500,h_400,c_fill,q_auto,f_auto/v1706000000/hotels/luxury-quad-room.jpg'
  WHEN id = 360004 THEN 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dqhct1qfx/image/upload/w_500,h_400,c_fill,q_auto,f_auto/v1706000000/hotels/standard-quad-room.jpg'
  WHEN id = 360005 THEN 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dqhct1qfx/image/upload/w_500,h_400,c_fill,q_auto,f_auto/v1706000000/hotels/family-room.jpg'
  WHEN id = 360006 THEN 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dqhct1qfx/image/upload/w_500,h_400,c_fill,q_auto,f_auto/v1706000000/hotels/single-room.jpg'
  ELSE images
END
WHERE id IN (360001, 360002, 360003, 360004, 360005, 360006)
